---
title: Grain, Bacon and Kale Harvest Super Salad with Spiced Sweet Potatoes
description: This nutty wild rice salad is the perfect combination of salty, sticky, sweet and crunchy. Roasted sweet potatoes and crisp chopped apples complete this stand-out supper salad.
